%TAG !u! tag:unity3d.com,2011:
--- !u!114 &11400000
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: e9620f8c34305754d8cc9a7e49e852d9, type: 3}
  m_Name: LocalizationTable_en
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Unity.Localization::UnityEngine.Localization.Tables.StringTable
  m_LocaleId:
    m_Code: en
  m_SharedData: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 5c0bc3c92bb249b4b85cdf57aecf7bf9, type: 2}
  m_Metadata:
    m_Items: []
  m_TableData:
  - m_Id: 43523039232
    m_Localized: Start game
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 43564982272
    m_Localized: Settings
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 43564982273
    m_Localized: Exit
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 43564982274
    m_Localized: Sound volume
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 43569176576
    m_Localized: Music volume
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 43569176577
    m_Localized: Press
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 43569176578
    m_Localized: to interact
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 43569176579
    m_Localized: Hold
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 43569176580
    m_Localized: to answer
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 43569176581
    m_Localized: Yes
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 43569176582
    m_Localized: No
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3002717757441
    m_Localized: The Empire's forces are currently evacuating the civilians. Our
      duty is to provide them with cover.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895159640100
    m_Localized: "\u2026"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 43581759499
    m_Localized: Dotinheim
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 43581759500
    m_Localized: Magginhall
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 43581759501
    m_Localized: Greenfall
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 43581759502
    m_Localized: The Ashen Sea
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 43581759503
    m_Localized: Command Headquarters
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 43581759504
    m_Localized: Old Bunker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 43581759505
    m_Localized: I`m here
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3002717757440
    m_Localized: Greetings, Sergeant. My name is Edward Dowell, I am the artillerist.
      You are my fire controller.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895151251456
    m_Localized: To begin, activate the map on the table. There should be a switch..
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895151251457
    m_Localized: Activated? Good.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895151251458
    m_Localized: Fire controller, you must provide me with enemy coordinates. The
      enemy is marked on the map with red dots.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895151251459
    m_Localized: When you see one - telegraph me immediately.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895151251460
    m_Localized: Don't even think of using the phone. The Command suspects wiretapping.
      Only the telegraph!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895151251461
    m_Localized: When you hear the sirens, it will mean that the enemy's attacking.
      Phone communications will be out immediately, so no use relying on them.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895151251462
    m_Localized: ':You''re in luck: there''s a wounded enemy on the battlefield.
      Still alive, but immobile'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895151251463
    m_Localized: At least you'll learn how it's done, before all hell breaks loose.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895151251464
    m_Localized: ':I repeat: when you see the red dot, do not hesitate and send me
      the coordinates immediately.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895151251465
    m_Localized: Well, I'll be damned. We've spent five years to capture this land.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895151251466
    m_Localized: And yet the enemy wipes out all fortifications in a matter of hours...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895151251467
    m_Localized: Be ready to send me the coordinates.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895151251468
    m_Localized: Good job, Sergeant! See, it ain't that hard. I'm no rookie myself
      - I've got your back.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895151251469
    m_Localized: I do wonder, does the young folk even know about the great conquests
      of the Empire?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895151251470
    m_Localized: What do they teach you about us at school?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895151251471
    m_Localized: ':Not much: just dates and the outcomes.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895151251472
    m_Localized: Seriously? They are raising a lost generation. Just so you know,
      we went through hell and back for the good of the Empire!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895151251473
    m_Localized: Every year, there's a special lesson. Not to mention my history
      teacher - he's obsessed with that era.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895151251474
    m_Localized: I'm glad to hear that. Good to know the country remembers our feat.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895151251475
    m_Localized: The battles raged at this very place. It has belonged to us for
      the longest time. The Empire becomes mightier thanks to people like you and
      I.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895151251476
    m_Localized: ...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895151251477
    m_Localized: Do you also have these posters? Who do you think are the monsters
      depicted on them?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895151251478
    m_Localized: No idea.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895151251479
    m_Localized: They're supposed to be us! What horrible faces! I'm no heartthrob,
      sure, but these make us out to be complete freaks!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895151251480
    m_Localized: Us?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895151251481
    m_Localized: That's right, sonny.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895151251482
    m_Localized: I only wonder if they had really seen us this way? Or was it just
      so the soldiers would fight better?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895151251483
    m_Localized: The Republic saw us as monsters. Still, it was them who set their
      own lands on fire just to smoke us out!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895151251484
    m_Localized: ':They made excuses! Said they didn''t have time to evacuate their
      civilians. The point is: they''ve destroyed everything they could get their
      hands on just so that we wouldn''t get it.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895151251485
    m_Localized: However it may be, we won. We've made these lands into our colonies.
      That's because our homeland is the greatest Empire of this era!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895151251486
    m_Localized: Crap! They are coming! Prepare to send the coordinates!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895151251487
    m_Localized: Looks like we held them off. Sergeant, you alive?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895151251488
    m_Localized: Yes.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895151251489
    m_Localized: Good to hear.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895151251490
    m_Localized: ...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895155445760
    m_Localized: Alright. You did well. Good job.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895155445761
    m_Localized: No.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895155445762
    m_Localized: Ha-ha. A joker, huh? I like that.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895155445763
    m_Localized: Who do you think we are fighting?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895155445764
    m_Localized: The Command stays silent and whoever I talk to doesn't know either.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895155445765
    m_Localized: What if it turns out there's no enemy at all? What if we're fighting
      among ourselves?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895155445766
    m_Localized: Hey, is your firing slit welded too?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895155445767
    m_Localized: Aye, sir. Not a hole, it's pretty stuffy in here.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895155445768
    m_Localized: Open the ventilation door sometimes. If you can even call it a door.
      Can't even fit a hand through there. Still, at least you'll get some fresh
      air.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895155445769
    m_Localized: Aye. Even light doesn't pass through.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895155445770
    m_Localized: You hang on in there. Everything feels pressing on you at first,
      then you get used to it. At least open the storeroom door sometimes. It will
      trick you into feeling there's more space.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895155445771
    m_Localized: ...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895155445772
    m_Localized: You've piled it on me, Sarge.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895155445773
    m_Localized: I'll go lay down.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895155445774
    m_Localized: My advice - you do the same. Haven't had a chance to sit down since
      arrival.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895155445775
    m_Localized: Sleep a bit or do something else. You'll need the stength.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895155445776
    m_Localized: Over.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895155445777
    m_Localized: So, Sergeant, got any sleep?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895155445778
    m_Localized: I didn't get much myself. Wish there was a pillow and a blanket.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895155445779
    m_Localized: And a good book. Discovered a writer recently, what's his name...
      Wells!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895155445780
    m_Localized: Now that fellow is a pro at making things u...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895155445781
    m_Localized: Come in, do you read me?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895155445782
    m_Localized: Commander Aiken speaking.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895155445783
    m_Localized: The enemy is currently at Dotinheim. They are currently undetectable
      by our radars. Still, we know for sure they are there.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895155445784
    m_Localized: Blanket the town with fire now. Otherwise, the enemy will get away.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895155445785
    m_Localized: I repeat - fire on Dotinheim. Begin at once.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895155445786
    m_Localized: Sergeant, what the hell do you think you are doing?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895155445787
    m_Localized: You want a military tribunal? Fine - I'll see to it. You'll end
      up cutting timber on a penal gang!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895155445788
    m_Localized: Mark my words - you won't get off easy!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895155445789
    m_Localized: Dowell, open fire!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895155445790
    m_Localized: You should thank Edward. You'd be executed this very day if not
      for him.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895155445791
    m_Localized: Return to your duty, immediately.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895155445792
    m_Localized: You won't have another chance.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895155445793
    m_Localized: Sergeant Dowell, congratualtions on the successful attack. The Motherland
      will not forget you.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895155445794
    m_Localized: This conversation is an exception. It won't happen again.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895155445795
    m_Localized: ':I once again remind you: using the phone during attacks is strictly
      prohibited!'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895155445796
    m_Localized: Over.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895155445797
    m_Localized: Hey, Sergeant, you did a great job.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895155445798
    m_Localized: Don't beat yourself up. Orders are orders.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895155445799
    m_Localized: Rookie, have you lost your mind?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895155445800
    m_Localized: An order's an order.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895155445801
    m_Localized: This is inhumane. There may have still been people left there.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895155445802
    m_Localized: Let's pretend I didn't hear that. What were you thinking when you
      applied for the army? We are killing people, not pushing forms.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895155445803
    m_Localized: If I hear anything like this again - I won't pity you and will report
      to the Command.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895155445804
    m_Localized: You are right. I should have done it.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895159640064
    m_Localized: That's what I like to hear. Now stop whining and do your job.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895159640065
    m_Localized: You won't last long here otherwise.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895159640066
    m_Localized: Hey, Sergeant, you there?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895159640067
    m_Localized: "I can\u2019t calm myself."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895159640068
    m_Localized: "There\u2019s something clawing at my heart."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895159640069
    m_Localized: I keep thinking about life back home - what's become of my house?
      What are the neighbours doing? Is the family safe?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895159640070
    m_Localized: "I know I shouldn\u2019t. But the harder I push the thoughts away,
      the more they press back."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895159640071
    m_Localized: Tell me about yourself, take the old man's mind off of things.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895159640072
    m_Localized: I applied for the army right after school.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895159640073
    m_Localized: Didn't lose any time, eh. Me too. After getting the graduation forms
      I went straight where the action was. Seen the world, got a medal.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895159640074
    m_Localized: Got back home. Had a hard time at first, but I got used to it.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895159640075
    m_Localized: I became a mechanic, worked at a factory. Now I got back into my
      uniform again and it feels like I never left.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895159640076
    m_Localized: When you get back, don't let yourself go mad. And if you got a girl
      - don't blame her. It's not her fault.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895159640077
    m_Localized: You went through your own hell, just like she - through her's. She's
      waiting for you, her heart in torment.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895159640078
    m_Localized: I've got a cat back home. Name's Fluffy.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895159640079
    m_Localized: There you go talking about home again! I asked you to talk about
      something else, didn't I?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895159640080
    m_Localized: ...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895159640081
    m_Localized: Five years ago, we got a dog. A little white one, hunts mice better
      than a cat!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895159640082
    m_Localized: My wife's a tailoress. Mimi's her main model. She'd always make
      her little costumes, hats. She used to make those for the kids, but they're
      all grown up now.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895159640083
    m_Localized: I keep telling her - why bother so much with the dog. But she just
      can't help it.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895159640084
    m_Localized: I say - let her do it, before she puts me in a bonnet.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895159640085
    m_Localized: ...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895159640086
    m_Localized: One time the coals in the fireplace got all cooled down, so Mimi
      snuck in there and slept through the night.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895159640087
    m_Localized: Scared the crap out of me. I go downstairs - and in the dark, all
      I see are her eyes and teeth.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895159640088
    m_Localized: We all laughed so hard that time.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895159640089
    m_Localized: ...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895159640090
    m_Localized: I hope we'll get home soon.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895159640091
    m_Localized: ...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895159640092
    m_Localized: Did you hear that?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895159640093
    m_Localized: What's happening?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895159640094
    m_Localized: What the...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895159640095
    m_Localized: Sergeant, this is commander Aiken speaking.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895159640096
    m_Localized: The evacuation of the civilians has been successfully completed.
      The Empire thanks you for your service.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895159640097
    m_Localized: ...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895159640098
    m_Localized: What the hell is this?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895159640099
    m_Localized: It's heading our way! Report to the Colonel!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895159640101
    m_Localized: Is everyone ok?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895159640102
    m_Localized: Fellows, stop panicking!  It's an unexploded shell.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895159640103
    m_Localized: It has a pretty weird shape, though.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895159640104
    m_Localized: ...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895159640105
    m_Localized: All command units, move to the bunker on level minus three. Immediately.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895159640106
    m_Localized: Forget the stupid papers! We're all about to die!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895159640107
    m_Localized: I repeat. All command units, move to the bunker on level minus three.
      Immediately.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895163834368
    m_Localized: Oh God!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895163834369
    m_Localized: AAAAAAAAA!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895163834370
    m_Localized: Hello? Sergeant?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895163834371
    m_Localized: You're a nice chap... We did a good job, you and I.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895163834372
    m_Localized: It hurts, for some reason. Guess I got them kidneys inflamed again.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895163834373
    m_Localized: Should've covered with a scarf, like my wife told me. Guess I was
      too dumb to listen.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895163834374
    m_Localized: Listen... Remember me on Day of Military Glory, will you?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895163834375
    m_Localized: See ya around... Sarge...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895163834376
    m_Localized: Fire controller! Open the door. Are you going to let me in?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895163834377
    m_Localized: Do you copy? Headquarters speaking.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895163834378
    m_Localized: The Command has suffered insignificant damage. The situation is
      under control.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895163834379
    m_Localized: Return to your duty.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895163834380
    m_Localized: Do you copy? This is Command Headquarters.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895163834381
    m_Localized: Sergeant, you must pay more attention..
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895163834382
    m_Localized: The last attack has considerably damaged the Headquarters building.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895163834383
    m_Localized: We won't last long. Please, protect us.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895163834384
    m_Localized: Sergeant! This is Command Headquarters.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895163834385
    m_Localized: "By your recklessness, you\u2019ve jeopardized the survival of not
      only the Command Headquarters, but the whole Empire!"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895163834386
    m_Localized: The situation's dire! The building is going to collapse any minute!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76895163834387
    m_Localized: Don't let these freaks bury us here!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1670395496030208
    m_Localized: Continue
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1671234927255552
    m_Localized: Language
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3985337234546691
    m_Localized: By the way, these used to be the Republic's bunkers. No one bothered
      to remove their posters.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3985337234546692
    m_Localized: I suppose, we never planned to stay here long.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3985337234546693
    m_Localized: Sergeant, are you insane? Had I listened to you now - the Empire
      would've been in ruins!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3985337234546694
    m_Localized: Try this again - you'll be court-marshalled in a blink of an eye!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3985337234546695
    m_Localized: 'Sergeant, let us hope this was a mistake. '
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3985337234546696
    m_Localized: The order to attack the Command Headquarters is equated to an assassination
      attempt.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3985337234546697
    m_Localized: All-clear, Sergeant, false alarm.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3985337234546698
    m_Localized: Game Over
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3985337234546700
    m_Localized: Sleep a bit or do something else. You'll need the stength.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3985337234546701
    m_Localized: Over.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3985337234546702
    m_Localized: Sleep a bit or do something else. You'll need the stength.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3985337234546703
    m_Localized: Over.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3985337234546704
    m_Localized: ...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3985337234546705
    m_Localized: ...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
